headline: Q2 Earnings Roundup: Colgate-Palmolive (NYSE:CL) And The Rest Of The Household Products Segment
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at household products stocks, starting with Colgate-Palmolive (NYSE:CL).
